    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's just math logic, isn't it?  it's not real life. in real life, if a zero disappears, the equation just gets simpler. there's no \"nudge,\" there's just less weight. it feels like it would actually be a relief to just... not be a variable anymore. to just be gone and have the noise stop.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
